Ask HN: How to find projects for my team
text: My team just finished a two year project.  And now we are without a project on hand.  We are doing a few small ones to keep busy but without a medium or big one on hand, I don’t think the team will be sustainable.  This tech recession is not ideal to lose a job.  I have been reaching out to other offices in other countries to see if we can help out.  What other advice would you give to find projects?
